blog.description: Probably going to be filled with Erasermic and My Hero Academia stuff, with a touch of other fandom things.

title: Poor tagging irritation rants.
body: Once again I’d just like to point out how terrible the tagging for this fandom is. I dare anyone to go into the Erasermic Tab on A03 and tell me how many fics that have almost nothing to do with Erasermic are there. If either Shouta or Hizashi aren’t the main focus of your story,aka it isn’t written from their perspective or they aren’t main focus of your story, DONT TAG ERASERMIC! add them as character but don’t add the tag their relationship as a main tag. It makes it so hard for those actually writing Erasermic to be seen over the sea of tododeku or bakudeku or whatever. There is still a serious Drought in the Erasermic tab and this makes it so much harder to find anything. Overall its just confusing. Sorry for the rant but ughh.
